title: SHOCK CHARGE! Missing-Mom-Hubby Fotis Dulos trade murder for alibi? DULOS LAWYER CHARGED RE: MURDER
itunes:title: SHOCK CHARGE! Missing-Mom-Hubby Fotis Dulos trade murder for alibi? DULOS LAWYER CHARGED RE: MURDER
description:
Did alleged wife killer Fotis Dulos plot to also murder his civil lawyer's wife? Bizarre voicemails are revealed following Dulos' arrest for the kidnapping and murder of his presumed-dead wife, Jennifer Dulos.

Joining Nancy Grace to discuss the case:

  • Troy Slaten: Criminal Defense Attorney 
  • Bobby Chacon: Former Special Agent FBI & current star of FB Watch Series "Curse of Akakor" 
  • Dr. Caryn Stark: Psychologist
  • Laura Ingle: Fox News National Correspondent
